OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy across the west with
OL,6,Fsome patchy light rain or drizzle.
OL,7,FMostly dry elsewhere with cloud
OL,8,Fbreaking to give some sunny spells by
OL,9,Fafternoon. Warm in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome brightness in the east
OL,12,Fthis evening. Otherwise a rather
OL,13,Fcloudy with patchy light rain in the
OL,14,Fwest. The east will remain largely
OL,15,Fdry. Freshening southwesterly winds in
OL,16,Fnorthwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
