OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FPatchy rain at first.
OL,6,FOtherwise dry and rather cloudy, some
OL,7,Fhazy sunshine developing in the east
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Some rain
OL,9,Fspreading east in the evening. Breezy
OL,10,Fin the north.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,13,Fspreading southeast on Saturday
OL,14,Fmorning, although light and patchy in
OL,15,Fthe east, then brighter with a few
OL,16,Fshowers. Mostly dry and bright Sunday.
OL,17,FChance of rain Monday in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
